<h2 class="bold font-l">Holo's true form</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Don't mess with the wolf goddess. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CanisMajor" class='trope-example-link'>Canis Major</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
